# ======================================================================
# PUBLIC repo (symbolic_pure_time): distribution-only. Keep it clean.
# Source, internal logs and notebook builders are NEVER published here;
# they live in the private `research` repo.
# ======================================================================

# --- LaTeX source: the public repo ships compiled PDFs, not sources ---
**/*.tex
**/*.bib

# --- notebook builders (the scripts that generate .ipynb) ---
tutorial/**/build_*.py
**/build_*_notebook.py
**/build_*walkthrough*.py

# --- internal development artifacts ---
**/notes/
**/previous_versions/
**/previous_rejected_work/
**/smoketests/
**/*_log.md
NEXT_SESSION.md
cover_letters/
highlights/

# --- LaTeX aux (regenerated on compile) ---
*.aux
*.log
*.bbl
*.blg
*.out
*.toc
*.synctex.gz
*.fls
*.fdb_latexmk

# --- python / Jupyter / OS ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.ipynb_checkpoints/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- paper PDFs: withheld until the paper formally enters review ---
papers/**/paper.pdf
Applications/**/paper.pdf
